The paper deals with the correspondence between levels of the Sherali-Adams relaxation of graph isomorphism and levels of pebble-game equivalence with counting, which involves combinatorics, linear algebra, and computational complexity. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CC (Computational Complexity), followed by cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics), cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), and cs.CG (Computational Geometry).
